Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:08.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:20.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:30.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are yo{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:31.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:34.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To the {\i1}To Hell With Dying{\i0} Warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:46.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's sudden, but won't you enlist with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Enlist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you're here means that you've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:55.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Um, I don't really understand what you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:57.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the world after death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:59.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do anything, you'll be erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:01.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Erased?  By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:03.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By God, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:06.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what do you mean by enlist?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enlist in the {\i1}To Hell With Dying{\i0} Warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:10.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the name of the unit changes sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:12.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously it was the Shinda Sekai Sensen, or the Afterlife Warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you go ahead and call it the afterlife...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:16.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it sound like you're accepting your death, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:18.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We changed the name because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:21.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and we're in the process of working on the new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:23.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's {\i1}To Hell With Dying{\i0} Warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:25.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, it was {\i1}Don't Feel Like I Was Ever Alive{\i0} Warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:27.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That came off as a bit of a joke, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:29.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So we changed it the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:30.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:33.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a real gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:38.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who comes here always asks that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:39.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to work on your adapability.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:41.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,React to things as they come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:44.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As they come to you... so what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:45.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:46.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:47.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:52.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's the enemy of the {\i1}To Hell With Dying{\i0} Warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:57.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought... {\i1}To Hell With Dying{\i0} still isn't working for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, start thinking of a better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:03.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, hey... no matter how you look at it, that's just a normal girl, isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this girl talking about?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:07.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.  Do you mind if I go over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:08.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:11.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?  Why the hell would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell makes you think that's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a complete idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:15.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Maybe I'll go see what dying's like"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:19.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"You wanna die?" is a common joke here in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:21.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?  You gonna laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:24.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The joke's fine.  More importantly, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:29.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like she'd make for a better conversation partner than the one aiming a gun at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your ally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:35.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell me not to point the gun, I won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:37.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Yurippe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:44.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the recruitment going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:49.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so low on members, we'll use whatever we can get!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:52.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going over there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!  My invitation didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:58.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't get what's going on at all...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with those people?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:03.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:11.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... you just had a gun aimed at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were saying you're an Angel or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:17.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?  I'm not an Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:19.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.  Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Student Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I'm too naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl was just teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:29.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.  I don't even know who I am, so I'm falling for stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, I'll just go to the hospital or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no hospitals here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody ever gets sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:38.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Never gets sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:40.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because everyone's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:49.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I've got it.  You're in on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to trick me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:54.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell... is this amnesia your doing, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:58.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Many people lose their memories when they come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you were in an accident and hurt your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:03.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then prove it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already dead, so I can't die, righ... {He's trailing off because she's moving towards him.  The "right" part of the sentence drops when he realizes what he just asked}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand-sonic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:11.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:27.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:37.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it hurt so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:51.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.  Shit!  I don't know what's going on, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you.  The one who insulted Yurippe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and spat on our warm welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:12.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey.  Wait.  Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:15.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:20.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very funny.  That's a joke in the afterlife, right?  Good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:21.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,100 Strikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:28.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Die die die die diediediediediediediediediediediedie diiiieee!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:33.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time you insult Yurippe, we'll dance again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.02,Signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,306)}A while later...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:43.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna kill me?  Talk about a sharp wit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:46.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of joke is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:50.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt so bad you could die, and then you can't!  This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}This is the world after death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do anything, you'll be erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:57.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!  I can just get erased!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do that, I can say goodbye to this crazy world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.84,Signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\pos(364,31.5)\frz359.12\frx348\fry0}Medical Office
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.84,Signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\fs24\frz357.83\frx346\fry356\pos(454,64.5)}School Infirmary Room 1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.84,Signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1D0A93&\fs27\org(418,602)\frx356\fry60\frz28.888\pos(416,588)}{\pos(180,552)}C\Nl\No\Ns\Ne\Nd
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.84,Signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\frz36.537\frx358\fry70\fs21\pos(490,592.5)}{\pos(1006,471)}Authorized \NPersonnel \NOnly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}I'm your ally, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}Have some faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone around here that looks trustworthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:10.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!  I'll look for an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:13.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But where are the adults?  The teachers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:14.85,Signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(654,496.5)\c&HBCB8B7&}Principal's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll ask the Principal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:20.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point... well then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're The One Who's Gonna Die{\i0} Warfront?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes it sound like {\i1}I'm{\i0} gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well of course we're talking about that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, well look this way, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:35.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}You're The One Who's Gonna Die{\i0} Warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:40.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... crap.  You're right; it does sound like I'm gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Any others?  Any good ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:47.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this one?  {\i1}Life Flashing Before Your Eyes{\i0} Warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's only the verge of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then how about this?  {\i1}Suicide Corps{\i0} Warfront. {Kesshitai is suicide corps, but he may be saying "want to erase"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:53.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you {\i1}want{\i0} to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:07:01.43,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh huh, oh yeah, that's right, oh yeah, oooh, nice
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stalemate{\i1} Warfront.  {This is a play on words.  The kanji for stalemate are "absolute end of life"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a stalemate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about, {\i1}Invincible Armada{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:06:59.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's not a warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:00.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dying Without Surrender{\i0} Squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:01.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think I won't punch you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{i1}The Wright Brothers{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:03.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystic Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to end with warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't surrender that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:10.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the front line of this battefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:12.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we come up with something more suitable?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that guy's awake now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:17.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Oh!  You're up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  I told him to think about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:24.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had plenty of time to think.  Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:28.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A new name for the {\i1}To Hell With Dying{\i0} Warfront, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do Whatever The Hell You Want{\i0} Warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh.  You've got some guts to go against Yurippe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, do whatever the hell you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drag me into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna disappear soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're still here, existing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:45.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I already explained it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:50.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to just meekly accept your erasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:50.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to meekly turn into a water flea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:53.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn righ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:54.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Water flea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:59.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?  You thought only humans had souls?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You might reincarnate as a corn barnacle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe as a hermit crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You might even be a wharf roach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:12.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so confused that you can't even joke about why we're only concentrating on sea creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, there's not really any reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:18.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought you'd just get out of here, go be a yes-man for the Angel and reach Nirvana, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'll become a corn barnacle and just get eaten by a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:23.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds great, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Corn barnacle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  You can eat those things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I never knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:31.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:36.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, everyone.  Let's not try to drive him out so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:41.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we of the... what are we now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Corn Barnacle{\i0} Warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! We of the {\i1}Corn Barnacl{\i0}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:48.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back!  Shinda Sekai Sensen! {Afterlife Warfront}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:49.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good kick...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're here in the Warfront's HQ, you'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew that and made your way here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:58.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no.  When I tried to enter, I suddenly found myself flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:02.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, in the next life, I might not be a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:02.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a joke at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but how would you even know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone come back and tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we can't check for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:14.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in Buddhism, there's no guarantee that one will be reincarnated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... a corn barnacle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, religious beliefs are just things that humans made up anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:24.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, listen well.  This is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:30.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the world we used to live in, "Death" was a random and indiscriminate visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we had no way to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this world is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:37.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, we can even go against the Angels, and continue to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:38.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:41.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, wait.  What will happen after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people after?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:47.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our objective is to erase Tenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, this world will be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:54.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You only arrived here recently.  It's no surprise that you're confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:58.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Work on your adaptability, and then react to things as they come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:02.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then... fight... Angels?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize.  Yuripp-whaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He got caught in his own trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That happened to me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:30.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You need a password in order to come in here safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:33.44,Signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(654,496.5)\c&HBCB8B7&}Principal's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:33.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the anti-Angel military headquarters, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other place where we can safely talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you stay here, go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the password?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:59.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No Angels, Gods, or Buddhas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yuri.  The leader of this warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, he's Hinata-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:09.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, he's pretty useless, but he has his moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Matsushita-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being ignored?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:17.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Fifth-rank in Judo, so he's well respected and we call him Matsushita-godan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:18.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meetcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:20.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ooyama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His distinguishing trait is his lack of distinguishing traits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the warfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.37,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I don't dance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.18,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how he says hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone calls him TK.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:33.26,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel the groove man.  Yeah.  Look inside yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows his real name.  He's a bit of a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:36.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay to hang with a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:40.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's always pushing up his glasses and sounding intellectual is Takamatsu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:41.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:42.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:43.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:45.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The last one is Fujimaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fujimaki, punk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:47.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a punk, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:50.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who went flying earlier is Noda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:53.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one in the shadows who keeps saying, "how foolish", is Shiina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:55.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting over here is Iwasawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:57.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the leader of the diversionary squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:12:03.03,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh huh, oh yeah, hmmm, yeahhhh, where's the beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:03.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not here right now, but we have dozens more members within the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:05.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which reminds me, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:11.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... um... uh... Oto... Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an amnesia-type, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:18.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it'll come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:20.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shouldn't we give him a uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:22.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right.  I'd forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:28.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, why is mine different than yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:31.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not different.  We're the ones who're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your outfit is for the "good" students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:38.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the uniform of the SSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.57,Eyecatch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(853,279)}{\blur1}UTW Presents:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.57,Eyecatch,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(853,279)}{\blur1}UTW Presents:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:56.50,Signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\fs30\pos(797,643)}Study Building A, Rooftop
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a huge campus, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have over 2,000 students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:58.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an enormous boarding school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world came up with{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:02.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.  Is it alright for us to talk here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, as long as it's not about operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel duped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:07.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:08.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's that?  Canned coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Key Coffee.  It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:13.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:16.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... no.  Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now is club activity time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:22.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys aren't gonna join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:24.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we did that, we'd disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:24.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:29.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we join in club activities and classes, we humans would disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:30.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like those guys aren't humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are just NPCs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,NPCs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know the term?  Non-Player-Characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a gaming term?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a metaphor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It means those guys have been in this world since the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So they have no self-consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:49.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like if I talked to them, they'd only repeat the same line?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:54.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still a newcomer, so you can't sense why we're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I converse with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:59.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go try and kancho one of the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kancho?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll probably run, or kick you or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:04.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pretty well-designed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:05.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The teachers, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:08.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.  Incidentally, the NPCs never age, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with Tenshi's brutality?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:17.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She stabbed me right after I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:20.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching that.  Wasn't that your own fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:24.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell an Angel to prove that you won't die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll just stab you right in the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:32.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From her perspective, it's just like if you asked where the teacher's lounge is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:35.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So Tenshi is obedient to the rules of this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More like she's just awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she self-conscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?  It's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:44.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of emotionlessness, bluntness, and lack of vocabulary...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she's more unique than the NPCs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is she usually able to kill so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, do things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:56.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For those students who don't engage in "proper" activities in school...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, she gives a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:01.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run, she'll chase you, then outrun you and block your path.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And use of force?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:04.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An eye for an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:05.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, whenever we've challenged her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:08.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's gotten you guys before too, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:12.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't even pretend to act like the good students.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those who disappeared for that, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, last question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does God exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, I've never seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you ever asked Tenshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:33.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Questions about this world are met with, "no comment".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:35.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The study session is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,375)}{\i1}To be honest, I'm not really planning to join their fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, I'm fighting for something more important.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:53.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just trying to buy enough time to safely recover my memories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:54.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's all there is to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,650)}{\i1}After that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:06.57,Signage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\pos(804,651)}Anti-Angel Operations HQ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Otonashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be new at this, but give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:10.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:12.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for her legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she can't pursue you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fighting against that girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't her injuries heal right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to learn from experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we've all come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:24.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good answer, Otonashi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:34.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The first order of business is to get you acclimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:37.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we'll be having you participate in a nice simple operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation will be called:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Operation Tornado.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, this sounds like a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T...Tornado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to steal lunch tickets from the students!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're stealing what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not big at all.  This is just petty bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:53.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:54.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got all these members and weapons for {\i1}this{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:58.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!  Are you trying to insult Yurippe again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:00.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:00.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:07.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We of the {\i1}Corn Barnacle Extinction{\i0} Warfront would never threaten students with power or superior numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:09.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going extinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:09.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:12.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said you were going to steal from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe we should have said "lift" the tickets. {this whole thing is a pun based on "makiageru".  It has multiple meanings.  Otonashi believes they are using the meaning of steal/rip off.  But they're actually using the meaning of "blow dust, etc into the air".  I'm using "lift" for this, as it's the only thing that carries the meanings of both raise and steal}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:18.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.  You're part of the barricade group that that will be stopping Tenshi's advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:21.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll surround the operation's target, the cafeteria...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, wait on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:26.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll put you somewhere easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:30.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk with Takamatsu-kun or Ooyama-kun for the rest of the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Iwasawa-san, I'm expecting another fine performance tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:33.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:36.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Tenshi appears, open fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be the signal for reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hear shooting, make sure you help out, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:46.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The operation will commence at 18:30.
