Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:12.08,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Play that Rock out for me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:14.97,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your eyes upon me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:17.80,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your eyes upon me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.52,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't even catch my breath inside of this town
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:26.45,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,The starry sky is our final stage
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:06.02,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away from here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.70,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away from here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:11.48,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,From now I will find you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:14.16,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,From now I will find you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:17.01,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Play that Rock out for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:19.69,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Play that Rock out for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:22.57,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing about love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:25.22,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sing about love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:27.94,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much time passes, I'll be right here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:30.71,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Passing right through everyone around me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:38.95,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you must be tired by now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.79,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if I'm only getting through to your back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:51.12,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,That song of light
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:57.88,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Play that song for me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Girldemo. {Girls Dead Monster}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.08,0:18:43.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The live show just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:30.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She appeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:33.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's here... she's coming towards me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:36.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does that mean I'm the weak point in this operation?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's belittling me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:40.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit!  I'll shoot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:44.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... a bullet into that delicate body?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:47.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't shoot,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:48.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she's gonna get me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without an ounce of mercy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:55.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... I wanted her legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't this good enough?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:03.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on{\fscx300}-
