Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:11.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:14.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't she stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:21.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:32.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh.  I missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:40.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.76,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,Give your little kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Going for our weakest member, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:46.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still only using Hand Sonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:47.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her into the open!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:49.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll attack in numbers as we pull back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:51.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Skill: Distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:56.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:02.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!  We're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:02.11,Dialogue-TK,,0000,0000,0000,,My god!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:03.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why guns are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:31.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!  What's going on with the lifting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just buying time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea it would be this epic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:43.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The show is at its apex.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:44.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Start it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:45.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Start it up, please.
