Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:23:02.31,Ending-Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I always walk all alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.32,0:23:09.71,Ending-Top,,0000,0000,0000,,When I turn around, everyone is far away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.63,0:23:17.50,Ending-Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of anything anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:26.29,Ending-Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(,800)}That's what I try to tell myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:37.35,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,)}Eventually, everyone will be alone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:45.13,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll continue to live only through their memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.17,0:23:52.81,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than try to love and laugh at this loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.84,0:23:59.36,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fight
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:07.75,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never show you my tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:22:57.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With this kind of power and leadership...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she could do whatever she wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:03.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's just sitting here relaxing and eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:06.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really have only one enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:08.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.19,0:23:10.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fighting against her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:14.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, are we really in the right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What we're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:17.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:19.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.89,0:23:20.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:25.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even have any memories, yet.
