Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:16.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c10: We call it a guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.72,0:24:16.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c147: It's your turn, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:16.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c71: Uaaaaaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.11,0:24:18.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c43: It seems you still don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.32,0:24:16.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c60: Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.58,0:24:18.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c37: The trap isn't disarmed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.04,0:24:18.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c83: Oh crap!  I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.04,0:24:19.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c182: Because you resisted at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:20.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c317: Tenshi is waking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.56,0:24:21.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c193: I don't know... I don't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.08,0:24:20.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c312: Shooooot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:21.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c347: What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.93,0:24:24.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,c211: You don't find a life like that to be unforgiveable?
